        public static java.lang.String pager(int maxPage,
                                     int currentPage,
                                     int range,
                                     java.lang.String url,
                                     java.lang.String pgPara)
        Generate a HTML page switcher list.
        Parameters:
        maxPage - (int) Last page value for this pager.
        currentPage - (int) Current page value.
        range - (int) Page switcher offset size.
        url - (String) Link url.
        pgPara - (String) Page's parameter name in url.
        Returns:
        (String) HTML Pageer text.
